Japan’s Maehara Calls for Phasing Out Nuclear Power, FT Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-07-03T21:07:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-03/japan-s-maehara-calls-for-phasing-out-nuclear-power-ft-says.html
Senior Japanese ruling party lawmaker
Seiji Maehara wants  Japan  to phase out nuclear power over the
next two decades and said that construction of new nuclear
reactors should “basically be stopped,” the Financial Times
reported, citing an interview with Maehara.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 